With regard to Tables (ref) \& (ref), advancing the use of KGs would help SEs to compute precise results to more complex queries, particularly multi-hop queries.
 Making this progress calls for enhancing the SEs' abilities for reliable entity recognition and disambiguation, and mapping phrases that denote types or predicates as well.